Big Brother Naija, BBNaija 2020 housemate, Dorathy has revealed details of the conversation she had with Brighto on Saturday night. Dorathy and Brighto engaged in a conversation on Saturday night after he told Ebuka that Dorathy has feelings for Ozo. However, Dorathy cleared the air to Brighto saying she does not have feelings for Ozo. Speaking to Lucy on Tuesday morning, Dorathy said Brighto told her he is in love with her. “Brighto said to me on Saturday night that he told Biggie he is in love with me (Dorathy) “He said he has not said it to anybody in the house but just me. “I feel he’s trying to play a game, he’s smart. “I’m not humiliating myself further in this house. I don’t know how to fight with girls.”